OL,3,CHouse arson and race-hate graffiti on
OL,4,C'much calmer' night of disorder
OL,6,FThere were "lower level disturbances"
OL,7,Fin Northern Ireland on Thursday night
OL,8,Fcompared with disorder over the
OL,9,Fprevious two nights, police have said.
OL,11,FThree arrests were made on a "much
OL,12,Fcalmer" night, one of which related to
OL,13,Fviolence on Wednesday night.
OL,15,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,16,F(PSNI) Assistant Chief Constable Ryan
OL,17,FHenderson said 19 arrests had now been
OL,18,Fmade since street violence first
OL,19,Ferupted on Tuesday.
OL,26,@nD@LOUnD@eO]sD@^OUtD@GO]
