OL,3,CHouse arson and race-hate graffiti on
OL,4,C'much calmer' night of disorder
OL,6,FDisorder flared in response to a knife
OL,7,Fattack on Monday night in which a man
OL,8,Fsuffering significant injuries,
OL,9,Fincluding the loss of his left eye.
OL,11,FStephen Ogilvie, who is in his 40s,
OL,12,Falso suffered deep cuts to his head,
OL,13,Fface and back in the stabbing attack
OL,14,Fin the north of the city.
OL,16,FOn Thursday it was said he remained in
OL,17,Fan induced coma, but his condition was
OL,18,Fsaid to be improving.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
