OL,3,CHouse arson and race-hate graffiti on
OL,4,C'much calmer' night of disorder
OL,6,FSudanese national Hadi Alodid, 30,
OL,7,Fappeared in court on Wednesday charged
OL,8,Fwith attempted murder over Monday's
OL,9,Fknife attack.
OL,11,FAlodid entered Northern Ireland across
OL,12,Fthe Irish border by bus in February
OL,13,F2023, having flown to Dublin from
OL,14,FParis.
OL,16,FHe then claimed asylum upon arrival
OL,17,Fand was granted leave to remain in the
OL,18,FUK until 2028.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
