OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781273476
OL,3,CHouse arson and race-hate graffiti on
OL,4,C'much calmer' night of disorder
OL,6,FOn Tuesday night, homes, a bus and
OL,7,Fcars were set on fire in Belfast, with
OL,8,Fpeople targeted based on their race.
OL,10,FWater cannons were deployed in Co
OL,11,FAntrim on Wednesday after police were
OL,12,Fpelted with bricks and a Department
OL,13,Ffor Infrastructure vehicle was left in
OL,14,Fflames. There was also serious unrest
OL,15,Fin Portadown, Co Armagh. Twelve police
OL,16,Fofficers were injured on Wednesday
OL,17,Fevening.
OL,19,FForeign national healthcare workers
OL,20,Fhave also been subject to threats and
OL,21,Fintimidation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
