OL,3,CHouse arson and race-hate graffiti on
OL,4,C'much calmer' night of disorder
OL,6,FA number of anti-racism events have
OL,7,Fbeen organised in response to the
OL,8,Funrest.
OL,10,FMr Henderson said: "There were
OL,11,Fpeaceful protests last night at a
OL,12,Fnumber of locations, including
OL,13,FNewtownabbey, with no significant
OL,14,Fincidents of public disorder. Officers
OL,15,Fengaged with participants supporting
OL,16,Ftheir right to express their views
OL,17,Flawfully.
OL,26,@rD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
