OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781273476
OL,3,CHouse arson and race-hate graffiti on
OL,4,C'much calmer' night of disorder
OL,6,F"Last night, officers were dealing
OL,7,Fwith some lower level disturbances and
OL,8,Fkeeping focus on patrols of key areas.
OL,9,FThere were three arrests in total
OL,10,Facross Northern Ireland ` one in
OL,11,Fconnection with disorder on Wednesday
OL,12,Fand including a man detained following
OL,13,Fcriminal damage to a vehicle in the
OL,14,FTaughmonagh area of south Belfast.
OL,16,F"There was an arson attack on a house
OL,17,Fin the Shore Road area of north
OL,18,FBelfast and reports of race-hate
OL,19,Fgraffiti in the Dee Street and
OL,20,FNewtownards Road area of east Belfast.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
