PN,44108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781273476
OL,3,CHouse arson and race-hate graffiti on
OL,4,C'much calmer' night of disorder
OL,6,F"A 27-year-old male threw a stone at a
OL,7,Fpolice vehicle during a mobile patrol
OL,8,Fin Abbeyville Court in Newtownabbey.
OL,10,F"He was arrested on suspicion of
OL,11,Fdisorderly behaviour.
OL,13,F"No significant disorder noted in
OL,14,FDerry/Londonderry overnight with one
OL,15,Farrest of a 16-year-old male for
OL,16,Friotous behaviour the previous night
OL,17,F(Wednesday)."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOU
