CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781273476
OL,3,CHouse arson and race-hate graffiti on
OL,4,C'much calmer' night of disorder
OL,6,FA car was set on fire in the Glenshane
OL,7,FRoad area of Derry after midnight on
OL,8,FFriday.JNo-one was injured but one
OL,9,Fvehicle was damaged in the fire which
OL,10,Fis being treated as hate-motivated
OL,11,Farson.
OL,13,FMr Henderson continued: "There have
OL,14,Fbeen 19 arrests so far this week with
OL,15,Fpeople already charged to court. Our
OL,16,Fpublic order inquiry team is working
OL,17,Fday and night to identify those who
OL,18,Fhave been involved in the disorder
OL,19,Fover the last number of days."
OL,26,@uD@YOU{D@^O]
